Online Thermometer
==================

Copyright 2009 Jonathan Oxer
Copyright 2009 Hugh Blemings

+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| This project is featured in the book "Practical Arduino" by         |
| Jonathan Oxer and Hugh Blemings (Apress, 2009). More information    |
| about the book and this project is available at:                    |
|                                                                     |
| www.practicalarduino.com/projects/easy/online-thermometer           |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------+

Install temperature sensors around your home or office and access an
up-to-the-moment report using a web browser. Readings can also be
logged and graphed over time.
